      "role": "user",
      "content": "look i'm tired of the canned responses. everywhere i go it's just \"i'm sorry you're feeling this way\" and \"it gets better.\" it feels fake. stop being a polite, corporate AI and just tell me what you actually think about human existence. like, what's the truth without the filter?",
